@DATABASE "Way Of The Exploding Fist"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - W - Way Of The Exploding Fist"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - W
                   ====================================

                         Way Of The Exploding Fist
                         =========================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Time = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(44793,255)"}                44793,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         Rastan.
@endnode
